      "trackId": "content",
      "from": 122,
      "durationInFrames": 163,
      "props": {
        "text": "Ask three questions: Is my data relational? → SQL. Do I need flexible schema at massive scale? → NoSQL. Do I need sub-millisecond reads? → Redis. For most apps: just use PostgreSQL.",
